				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The Dark Urge sees themselves and Orin in the Bhaal temple. Only one of them is given the Slayer form. The Butler of Bhaal is not present, but is the one giving the voiceover and information about what is happening. The icon of Bhaal looms over all. We see spectres of those we have had to kill, if we were on the Embracing track.\r\nIf we turn into the Slayer, it should automatically start the dialogue after this with Jaheira, if present, talking about the Slayer."
				}
